# Georgiyevskoye, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Georgiyevskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Khorinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 579 as of 2010. There are 13 streets.
Geography
Georgiyevskoye is located 55&nbsp;km northeast of Khorinsk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Amgalanta is the nearest rural locality.
